==English==
===Alternative spellings===
*sometimes hyphenated or expressed as a phrase: '''poly-deistically''', '''poly deistically'''
*sometimes either the P or both the P and the initial T are capitalized: '''Polydeistically''', '''PolyDeistically'''
*variations of capitalization and spacing may be combined: '''Poly-deistically''', '''Poly-Deistically''', '''Poly Deistically''', '''Poly deistically'''
===Adverb===
{{en-ad|polydeistically}}
'''polydeistically'''
# in a [[polydeistic]] manner

